                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12610591" author="daveel" created="Fri, 4 Jul 2008 14:13:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Do you know which revisions fixed this problem. I&apos;m having the same issue with binding files specified as relative paths.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12611228" author="dkulp" created="Mon, 7 Jul 2008 16:45:38 +0000"  >
&lt;p&gt;That&apos;s because binding files are specified as &quot;extra args&quot; that we really make no attempt to parse and process.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve updated the plugin to allow&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;bindingFiles&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;bindingFile&amp;gt;path/to/file.xjb&amp;lt;/bindingFile&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/bindingFile&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To pull them out of the extraArgs and process them properly in the mojo.   &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ideally, we&apos;d pull all the useful flags out of extraArgs.   extraArgs should be a last resort thing, not a primary thing.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
